{
  "stem": "3100.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So therefore, take along your most precious possessions and come out to the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And whoever will disobey this law will be immediately shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And this they go around with speakers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And you're debating whether you should go out from the house or not.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There comes another order.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We will come into the houses.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Whoever will found in the house, somebody will be immediately shot.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Take along your most precious possessions and come out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And as we looked out through the window, there were a few already people shot that ran, that weren't in their homes, or were at a neighbor's house.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "If they got across the street, they shot them right away.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And of course, this spread a lot of--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Terror and fear among us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what do you think my parents grabbed?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father took his prayer shawl and tefillin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My mother took her little two candlesticks and candles that wherever we come, at least we should be able to observe-- Shabbos.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Shabbos and first mitzvah, mitzvot that were-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember that have we have any bread at that time, because we had left a few pieces of matzah, and they took along with them.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we got into the marketplace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shall I explain to you what happened?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When were get in the marketplace, I came out and I showed them my certificate that I worked the Commander, for the German Commander, so they let me out.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I thought that I'll be able to pull along a few members of my family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was utterly shut off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On the other side, I couldn't take anybody.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that was the last time I saw my parents and my sisters and brother.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
